name: Rick Grimes
description: A former sheriff's deputy who becomes the leader of a group of survivors in a zombie apocalypse.

name: Michonne
description: A fierce and skilled warrior who becomes a valued member of the survivor group led by Rick Grimes.

name: Tallahassee
description: A cynical and tough survivor who is on a mission to find the last Twinkie in a world overrun by zombies.

name: Shaun
description: An unambitious sales clerk who must rally his friends and family to fight off a zombie invasion in London.

name: Alice
description: A former security officer who battles zombies and other biological monstrosities created by the Umbrella Corporation.

name: Columbus
description: A college student who has managed to survive in a world overrun by zombies by following a strict set of survival rules.

name: Selena
description: A tough and resourceful survivor who teams up with a small group of people in a world devastated by a viral outbreak.

name: Jill Valentine
description: A skilled member of S.T.A.R.S. who battles the undead and other bioweapons in a variety of dangerous situations.

name: Terry Chen
description: A delivery driver who becomes a reluctant hero in a world where the sun has turned people into zombie-like creatures.

name: Maggie Greene
description: A farm girl who becomes a skilled fighter and leader in a group of survivors trying to rebuild after a zombie apocalypse.

name: Peter
description: A member of a group of survivors who takes refuge in a shopping mall during a zombie outbreak, but becomes infected and turns into a zombie.

name: Shaun Riley
description: A photojournalist who must navigate a mall filled with zombies and rescue survivors in order to uncover the truth behind the outbreak.
